    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "I Like the teacher interact with the children.  About how they clear all our doubts .",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the college premises take care of students need they focus on real education.  Whatever they are giving to us is really helpful",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "They offer up scholarship which good for students",
          "name": "Abhishek Dwivedi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Library staff is very good and they have many book's for students.",
          "name": "Rudrakshi agnihotri",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Regular co curriculum activity happened to increase extra knowledge",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Facility, big class room , parking , teacher",
          "name": "Nitesh Dubey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The Sports ground conditions is too good and everything is maintained in sports Authority.",
          "name": "SHIV SAGAR DUBEY",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching experience of teachers is really good",
          "name": "Aman Singh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like examinations process as it is very well organised.",
          "name": "Suryakant Rana",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I liked cocurricular activites being conducted in college",
          "name": "Sumit Rana",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "I Don't like the walls of our classroom thar it should be maintained descently.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "A student's attendance is very necessary.  I think the government should take care of this problem that they should supervise if the child is attending all the classes regularly or not.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "M.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "They charge money to park vehicle in college",
          "name": "Abhishek Dwivedi",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus is soo big that leads to create trouble to find class",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Thing I don't like about vssd college is lack of focus on extra curricular activities",
          "name": "Nitesh Dubey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "I am boy and I face lots of problems in terms of practical and other exam information",
          "name": "Nitesh Dubey",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "parking system",
